        - New table: `financial_statement` with JSON column for 180+ numeric fields
        - Design rationale: JSON storage avoids 180-column wide table; single table serves all statement types for extensibility
        - UNIQUE KEY on (source, symbol, market, statement_type, reporting_period, report_type, statement_code) ensures upsert idempotency
        - New model: `FinancialStatement`, `FinancialStatementFilters`
        - New DAO/Service/Controller: `FinancialStatementDao`, `FinancialStatementService`, `FinancialStatementController`
        - New API endpoints:
            - `POST /api/v2/financial/{source}/{statement_type}/upsert`
            - `GET  /api/v2/financial/{source}/{statement_type}?symbol=...&period_start=...&period_end=...`
        - Registered components: `dao_financial_stmt`, `svc_financial_stmt`, `ctrl_financial_stmt`
        - New reference constants (`internal/consts/financial.go`):
            - `FIN_STMT_*`: statement type identifiers
            - `REPORT_TYPE_*`: Q1/H1/Q3/Annual (报告期名称 1-4)
            - `STMT_CODE_*`: statement codes 1-10 (合并报表/母公司报表 variants)
            - `PROFIT_NOTICE_*`: 业绩预告类型代码 1-11
        - Updated `0001_init.sql` migration with new table definition
    - Added corporate action support (dividend / right_issue):
        - New table: `corporate_action` with JSON column for variable data fields
        - UNIQUE KEY on (source, symbol, market, action_type, report_period, ann_date) ensures upsert idempotency
        - New model/DAO/Service/Controller: `CorporateAction*`
        - New API endpoints:
            - `POST /api/v2/corporate-action/{source}/{action_type}/upsert`
            - `GET  /api/v2/corporate-action/{source}/{action_type}?symbol=...&period_start=...&period_end=...`
        - New reference constants (`internal/consts/corporate_action.go`):
            - `CORP_ACTION_*`: action type identifiers
            - `DIV_PROGRESS_*`: dividend progress codes 1-19
            - `RI_PROGRESS_*`: right issue progress codes 1-22
- v1.1.0
    - Added industry constituent and weight data support:
        - New tables: `industry_constituent`, `industry_weight`, `industry_daily`
        - New models: `IndustryConstituent`, `IndustryWeight`, `IndustryDaily`
        - New API endpoints:
            - `POST /api/v2/taxonomy/{source}/industry-constituents/upsert`
            - `GET  /api/v2/taxonomy/{source}/industry-constituents/by_index/{indexCode}`
            - `GET  /api/v2/taxonomy/{source}/industry-constituents/by_stock/{conCode}`
            - `POST /api/v2/taxonomy/{source}/industry-weights/upsert`
            - `GET  /api/v2/taxonomy/{source}/industry-weights/{indexCode}?trade_date=...`
            - `POST /api/v2/taxonomy/{source}/industry-daily/upsert`
